# Backup Folder Structure

Correct structure:

```
MongoBackup/
│
├── Copilot/
│   ├── Campaign.bson
│   ├── Campaign.metadata.json
│   ├── Users.bson
│   └── ...
│
├── Admin_Central/
│
├── admin/
│
└── node-boilerplate/
```

Each folder = Database

Each .bson file = Collection

---

# MongoDB Structure

```
MongoDB Server
│
├── Database
│     ├── Collection
│     │      ├── Document
│     │      ├── Document
│     │      └── Document
│     │
│     └── Collection
│
└── Database
```

---

# SQL vs MongoDB

| SQL | MongoDB |
|------|----------|
| Server | Server |
| Database | Database |
| Table | Collection |
| Row | Document |
| Column | Field |
| Primary Key | _id |

