# Notes

- One MongoDB server can contain many databases.
- Default local port is **27017**.
- Use **mongodump** to export databases.
- Use **mongorestore** to import databases.
- Compass is only a GUI. It does not run the MongoDB server.
- Database Tools are utilities only. They do not run the MongoDB server.
